node.text:
Come behind the scenes with us at our recent #EveryBODYinPLT Unfiltered Swim shoot 🤩🌴 

Entirely shot on a smartphone with no filters necessary, every body is beach body ready 🔥 Who else is obsessed with our dream dolls?! @natalie_amber1, @terrili, @zoe_mariedavies, @strongsassysavage, @misstalulaheve & @imogenfkingivy 👏💗

#btsphotoshoot #beachbodyready #bodyappreciation #swimwearinspo #summergirls #behindthescenesvideo #summeroutfits
